version_description: Capo on 4th fret, 4 chord song, Easy for beginners.

Here are the chords for American Author's song "Pride", based off the studio version. you can play along with it here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_guBE6TBhoM. there's a capo on 1st fret for simpler chords- enjoy :)).

I have looked at all of the tabs for this song and the only one that is close is Version 3. I am not saying that the others are wrong but maybe slightly misleading to a beginner. I just think that these chords work and gel together ........
